import * as React from 'react'
import { Flex, Heading, Input, Grid, GridItem, Box } from '@chakra-ui/react'

const PokeDex = () => (
    <Flex height='100vh' alignItems='center' justifyContent='center'>
        <Flex height='80%' width='80%' background='red.300' p={10} rounded={6}>
            <Grid templateColumns="repeat(5, 1fr)" w='100%' gap={4}>
                <GridItem rounded={5} colSpan={3} h="100%" bg="white" p={4}>
                    <Heading>PokeDex</Heading>
                    <Input placeholder="Pikachu" variant='filled' mb={3} />
                </GridItem>
                <GridItem rounded={5} colSpan={2} h="100%" bg="white" />
            </Grid>
        </Flex>
    </Flex>
)

export default PokeDex
